  "title": "🚀 Event Marketing & Sales Trainee – Real Campaigns, Real Growth ☄️",
  "description": "<p><em><strong>Event Marketing & Sales Trainee (ENTRY LEVEL)</strong></em></p><p>Looking for a job that actually levels you up? Join Ascend Marketing Solutions and dive into high-energy events, brand activations, and face-to-face sales. This is performance-based, with uncapped earnings and fast-track growth. Grind hard, get rewarded, and move up fast.</p><p><u>You will:</u><br /><br />✨ Lead live campaigns & activate premium brands</p><p>✨ Build relationships & sell experiences that matter</p><p>✨ Learn from top performers & gain real hands-on skills</p><p><u>We want:</u></p><p>⚡ Energetic, coachable, and ambitious hustlers</p><p>⚡ Confident communicators who love people</p><p>⚡ Mindset over experience! your drive > your resume</p><p><u>Why Ascend?</u></p><p>💰 Unlimited earning potential</p><p>🚀 Fast promotions based on results</p><p>🌟 Premium brand exposure & real events</p><p>🎉 Fun, high-energy team culture</p><p><em><strong>Ready to grind, grow & get rewarded? This is your launchpad.</strong></em></p>",
